  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 360 to define \"medical debt\"; establish a maximum interest rate of 3% on medical debt; amend KRS 360.020 to expand the civil penalty for excessive interest on medical debt; amend KRS 360.040 to establish a maximum interest rate of 3% on judgments rendered in an action to collect medical debt; make technical amendments; amend KRS 216B.250 to conform."
    }
  ],
